               <p>THIRD COUNT, the same, only stating them to be the property of the 
               <persName id="t18230115-1-victim65" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t18230115-1-viclabel4" type="occupation">keepers of His Majesty's Mints of his Cities of London and Canterbury</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230115-1-victim52 t18230115-1-viclabel4"></join>
