            . I am senior moneyer of <placeName id="t18230115-1-crimeloc5">the Mint</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18230115-1-crimeloc5" type="placeName" value="the Mint"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18230115-1-crimeloc5" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230115-1-off1 t18230115-1-crimeloc5"></join>. The others are 
               <persName id="t18230115-1-person67">
