                     <interp inst="t18230115-1-person75" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was formerly a silversmith. On the 10th of December, I attended the Mint with my son-in-law Mr. Field; whose account is perfectly correct.</p>
               <p>MR. CALRS 
               <persName id="t18230115-1-person76">
                  EDWARD 
                  POWELL
               <interp inst="t18230115-1-person76" type="surname" value="POWELL"></interp>
