                  </persName>
            . I am assistant to the solicitor of the Mint. I took down before the Magistrate<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182301150004"></xptr>the evidence of the witnesses, and after the examinations were read, Mr. Twyford asked the prisoner what he had to say (what he said was not taken down); he said,</p>
               <p>"
               <persName id="t18230115-1-person77">
                  Samuel 
                  Marlow
               <interp inst="t18230115-1-person77" type="surname" value="Marlow"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230115-1-person77" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230115-1-person77" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
